{"tid":1448614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:18.000Z","uid":95181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"275f79af3770daf6b71ba404299b78c7f8f9b54a","tid":1448614,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:20.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=d6b107da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=0d8aea97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"f8d176b7de193306400ac6690a896e2462efeb4b","tid":1448614,"uid":180039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGHvq2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGHvq2i.jpg&h=143095c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8fb83a4ee4ae7778843a8bdf91fd21b23930cfd","tid":1448614,"uid":285446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証"}]}